{"tid":526002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 拖欠員工40萬薪金　沙中線工程分判商拒認罪","createTime":"2018-01-11T09:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-11T09:17:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4052ab99bff746a30d9b11d3757f08fd0562b991","tid":526002,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T09:12:22.000Z","msg":"港鐵沙中線兩個工程地盤及中環灣仔繞道工程地盤上年爆發工潮，分判商碧海土木工程有限公司被指拖欠薪金。該公司今(11日)在觀塘裁判法院被勞工處票控18項欠薪罪，涉及6名員工，合共約40多萬工資，被告公司<span style=\"color: red;\">否認全部控罪</span>，案件押後今年3月8日預審。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180111/bkn-20180111162812336-0111_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180111%2Fbkn-20180111162812336-0111_00822_001.html&d=OqOhahmz45aXQeCbXoL6R0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=6f9daede\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180111/bkn-20180111162812336-0111_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e41681eab3a84600422dfe6568e9ed6d34b42c74","tid":526002,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T09:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9164435e5d290048b3ee5eb5b959c1376b8b8c41","tid":526002,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T09:13:15.000Z","msg":"返工=社會服務令<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18346f679f247d7fa144efca381c27847ef69b4","tid":526002,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T09:17:05.000Z","msg":"有出入閘紀錄都可以唔認？"}]}